Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Operated under the renowned Quest brand

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Quest Fremantle is located at the heart of the Port City, only metres from the Fremantle Train station and 22km south west of the Perth CBD.

Perfectly positioned within the West End historical precinct, amongst restaurants, galleries, retail outlets and the numerous buildings of Notre Dame University, 8 Pakenham Street was redeveloped in 2016 into the exceptionally well presented 122 key apartment hotel. 

Cleverly designed, the building complements its modern aesthetic and hotel amenity against its heritage facade that is well suited to the historical precinct. 

Renowned as Western Australia’s premier tourist destination behind the Perth CBD, the historic city attracts year-round demand from tourists and locals alike. With domestic travel restrictions starting to lift, we expect WA and Fremantle to be at the forefront of domestic travellers minds as they look to holiday away from home, but within Australia, for the foreseeable future. Quest Fremantle offer the flexibility to service the high demand for travellers with either short or extended stay requirements. 

Operated under the Quest brand, the leading serviced apartment hotel operator in the Asia Pacific region. Quest is a member of The Ascott Limited (Ascott), a Singapore company that has grown to become one of the leading international lodging owner-operators.  

Quest Fremantle is offered For Sale via an Expressions of Interest campaign closing 29th June 2021 at 3:00pm (AWST).

CBRE is proud to present for sale 50-60 and 62-68 Queen Victoria Street, Fremantle for sale by Offers to Purchase.

- Northern gateway entrance to the Fremantle city centre and waterfront precincts
- Exceptional footprints for large scale development, potential for 8-10 storeys
- Two distinct lead corner, elevated land parcels of 3,464sqm* and 7,594sqm* (Subject to 1,310sqm* site acquisition)
- Larger site is subject to 1,310sqm* acquisition of surplus Government land
- Breathtaking active Fremantle Harbour and Indian Ocean coastal views
- Directly adjacent to award winning Heirloom Apartments waterfront project 
- Favourable planning scheme provides for mixed use high-rise development
- Ideal location for a blend of retail, hotel and mixed use residential apartments 
- Residual lease to leading Holden dealership until strategic relocation

For further information contact the CBRE exclusive agents.
